{"tid":439859,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳寶安紅衣少女雨夜中被撞飛身亡  「司機太冤枉」掀駡戰","createTime":"2017-10-18T08:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T08:40:38.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"94a0bd050c6061455ba133292139ba073d8e7ce9","tid":439859,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:06:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171017/large/1508249281_30c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171017%2Flarge%2F1508249281_30c3.jpg&h=61673ee4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=USYxeI1IE6o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUSYxeI1IE6o&d=3l%2FqZyfP6LRDkR2YTTFA0zACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=57875651\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=USYxeI1IE6o</a><br />\n周一（16日）晚，下雨天，深圳寶安發生恐怖車禍。胡姓男司機駕車沿107國道北行至福永稔田人行天橋路段時，一名身穿紅衣裙少女突然出現在車前，被撞後在空中打轉，然後墮地，滑行10多米後，當場死亡。這宗奪命交通意外，事後因雙方責任問題，引發網民爭議。<br />\n<br />\n影片顯示，事發時正下着毛毛細雨，胡男粵Y號私家車在公路上行駛，汽車水撥不斷擺動，路面幾乎沒有其他車輛。豈料當車駛至稔田人行天橋路段時，一名身穿紅裙的長髮女，突然出現在司機眼前，她正背對汽車在車道上行走，他立即煞車，但已來不及，女子被撞飛，先在空中打轉一圈後落地，再在路上滑行10多米才停下。救護員到場後，證實該名女子已當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n據深圳交警通報，胡男通過酒精測試，結果顯示其體內酒精濃度為0，並無酒駕。目前，事故仍在調查中。事件曝光後，網民卻就責任問題掀起罵戰，有網民認為司機沒錯，「紅衣女幹嗎要在機動車道走啊 」，根本是「自殺」行為，加上當時路面幽暗，司機未必能看到路況：「不是快撞上我也沒看到有人&hellip;這司機太冤枉了」。不過亦有人卻提出相反意見，支持紅衣女沒錯，「司機一點也不冤枉，視線不佳時司機是需要減速慢行確保安全的，」另有網民稱，問題與警方在路上安裝的相機燈光，影響司機視線；故提出：「裝個行車記錄儀了，不然這司機可說不清了」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20171018/57344293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20171018%2F57344293&d=3l%2FqZyfP6LRDkR2YTTFA0zACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=e2db93ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20171018%2F57344293&h=517586e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20171018/57344293</a>"},{"pid":"156d74ffffd358fa8e667efc462576dcc0f9f88e","tid":439859,"uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:07:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">周一（16日）晚</span><br />\n<br />\n十九大前兩日撞死人 司機RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce7916c39b7a0c1ba3a9233e7d46990edb2a49a","tid":439859,"uid":51978,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:13:11.000Z","msg":"無端端喺馬路中間行唔係自殺係乜"},{"pid":"6ec10f336d5dd90b6ae138b4945808eb257e528b","tid":439859,"uid":105498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:14:19.000Z","msg":"以為係司機見到紅衣女諗做係女鬼<br />\n嚇到一野車埋去，之後話冤枉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0392ce571217020f20b4afebe71115320398b9ed","tid":439859,"uid":51978,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:14:30.000Z","msg":"睇片可直接飛去第10秒"},{"pid":"fbc55a5108c2e10940a4a5198e3801a4c07ff6f2","tid":439859,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:14:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8617066c6c3cff5b627703d5b8f311dcaaaa90e1","tid":439859,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:17:19.000Z","msg":"女鬼？"},{"pid":"8cc0941563fc5c3a345c850f14aa313e58392e31","tid":439859,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:18:37.000Z","msg":"當然係司機錯<br />\n<br />\n車速太高，<br />\n壓中間白線，即係過咗界，人哋如果正常過馬路一樣比佢車死。"},{"pid":"30901bd7f4cf59a40ac4bf9329b41dd96b097845","tid":439859,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:20:50.000Z","msg":"黑底底女屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue